OL,3,CWoman struck by tree being felled left
OL,4,Cwith traumatic brain injury
OL,6,F"There were school children at the
OL,7,Fforest when we were there and we are
OL,8,Frelieved that our accident didn't
OL,9,Fhappen to them. Ken and I hope an
OL,10,Fincident like this never happens
OL,11,Fagain."
OL,13,FMr Leafe suffered cuts and bruising.
OL,15,FA Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,16,Finvestigation found The Conservators
OL,17,Fof Ashdown Forest failed to identify
OL,18,Fthe risk to members of the public from
OL,19,Ftree felling.
