OL,4,Cwith traumatic brain injury
OL,6,FHSE principal inspector, Emma Stiles,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Members of the public should be
OL,8,Fable to enjoy a walk in a forest
OL,9,Fwithout fear of being struck by a tree
OL,10,Fbeing felled.
OL,12,F"The guidance is clear on how to fell
OL,13,Ftrees safely and this means keeping
OL,14,Fmembers of the public out of an area
OL,15,Faround the tree measuring two times
OL,16,Fthe height of the tree.
