OL,3,CWoman struck by tree being felled left
OL,4,Cwith traumatic brain injury
OL,6,F"This can be achieved by various means
OL,7,Fincluding signs, barriers and
OL,8,Fbanksmen. Given the high levels of
OL,9,Fpublic access around this tree, all of
OL,10,Fthese precautions should have been
OL,11,Ftaken."
OL,13,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,14,FAshdown Forest said: "We fully accept
OL,15,Fthe findings of the HSE investigation
OL,16,Finto the events of 25 January 2023
OL,17,Fwhen a member of the public was struck
OL,18,Fby a falling tree.
