OL,6,F"We have implemented all their
OL,7,Frecommendations including and
OL,8,Fexceeding their advice on training for
OL,9,Fall staff and volunteers operating in
OL,10,Fsafe working zones.
OL,12,F"We apologise unreservedly to Mr and
OL,13,FMrs Leafe and their friends and family
OL,14,Fwho were impacted by this incident and
OL,15,Fcontinue to send our best wishes to
OL,16,FMrs Leafe as she continues her
OL,17,Frecovery."
